Package pl.put.poznan.buildinginfo.logic

Class MainTransformer

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.put.poznan.buildinginfo.logic.MainTransformer
  • @Component
public class MainTransformer
extends Object
    The MainTransformer class is responsible for managing a collection of buildings. It provides methods to add, retrieve, and search buildings, floors, and rooms by their IDs.
